Text:
Thank you for giving links to my torrents... :)

Seed away!

No offense intended, but in my opinion these are NOT the best videos from those torrents.  

I guess it's always a matter of taste, but you have included videos that I find totally boring (and are surely fake "hidden camera" videos) and you have not included a ton of the most amazingly hot videos from the original series of torrents.

A word of advice to others, check out the original torrents, and hand-select your own "best".  It's actually an enjoyable exercise, and you won't miss some amazing videos not included here on this torrent...

Still, thanks to the uploader for the effort.
